WEBVTT

1
00:00:07.799 --> 00:00:10.148
[GROWLING]

2
00:00:14.614 --> 00:00:18.643
My ear. My fucking ear.

3
00:00:18.684 --> 00:00:21.064
[SCREAMS]

4
00:00:23.853 --> 00:00:25.693
[GROANING]

5
00:00:26.973 --> 00:00:28.546
[GROWLING]

6
