<i>ROSIE [OVER RADIO]: Detective Bellefleur.
we've got a 586 in progress in Hotshot.</i>

830
00:49:49.189 --> 00:49:53.626
Uh. Rosie. you realize a 586
means illegal parking? Over.

831
00:49:53.660 --> 00:49:57.295
<i>Oh. I could have sworn
that's what Kenya said.</i>

832
00:49:57.330 --> 00:49:59.197
<i>Anyway.
they're busting a meth lab.</i>

833
00:49:59.231 --> 00:50:02.633
<i>whatever the code is for that.
Over.</i>

834
00:50:04.335 --> 00:50:06.236
Wanna take a drive?

835
00:50:08.338 --> 00:50:10.440
JASON: Huh.
I ain't never been to Hotshot.

836
00:50:10.475 --> 00:50:13.611
ANDY:
Nothing to write home about.

837
00:50:18.149 --> 00:50:20.817
