894
00:53:43.488 --> 00:53:45.856
So romantic.

895
00:53:45.890 --> 00:53:49.592
It's not romantic.
it's delusional.

896
00:53:49.627 --> 00:53:51.160
[RUSSELL CHUCKLES]

897
00:53:51.194 --> 00:53:54.730
RUSSELL: Lorena.
Oh. goodie.

898
00:53:54.764 --> 00:53:56.998
I'm just in time for dessert.

899
00:53:59.101 --> 00:54:00.434
[BILL GROWLS]

900
00:54:00.469 --> 00:54:04.203
[SCREAMING]

901
00:54:10.610 --> 00:54:13.978
To have and to hold.

902
00:54:14.012 --> 00:54:16.647
to love and to cherish.

903
00:54:16.681 --> 00:54:21.051
to blah. blah. blah. blah. blah.
until death do you part.

904
